From David Fuess Subject MathCad vs NDW I just got off the phone with Mathsoft technical They are now admitting a problem of unknown nature with Maple and Norton Desktop for They have no clue at this time and are collecting configuration information on the systems which exhibit the Anyone having problems loading the Maple solver in MathCad under NDW shoud call technical support at They made no schedule promices but are actively working on the In the meantime the workaround is to provide a configuration selection in to use PROGMAN yuk pew whenever you plan to use the Maple solver and NDW I am using Norton BE to place a little menu on the screen with a second timeout to auto boot David Fuess Dir Center for EECS Phone Fax Lawrence Livermore National Laboratory